│ operands in select arms and if both arms simplify to the same value, returns  │
│ the false arm.\n\n3. Root Cause Analysis:\nThe function                       │
│ simplifySelectWithICmpCond applies equivalence-based simplification for any   │
│ ICmp eq, including pointer equality. Specifically, for Pred == ICMP_EQ, it    │
