│ provenance: choosing the other operand may change the pointer                 │
│ identity/provenance even if addresses are equal. The documentation comment    │
│ above simplifySelectWithEquivalence says it is intended for integer equality  │
│ or floating-point equivalence. However, the current code path incorrectly     │
│ uses it for pointer equality, because m_ICmp matches pointer compares         │
