│ simplifySelectWithEquivalence for ICMP_EQ, add a check to ensure              │
│ CmpLHS->getType()->isIntOrIntVectorTy(). If the type is pointer (or           │
│ non-integer), skip the equivalence substitution block.\n\nEdit at             │
